        {
            "title": "人行：今年仍有減息降準空間",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">人民銀行副行長鄒瀾表示，今年仍有一定減息降準空間，目前法定存款準備金率平均6.3%，降準仍有空間。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"鄒瀾 (圖片來源：中國網)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250714_FI_source-web_CL.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"鄒瀾 (圖片來源：中國網)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250714_FI_source-web_CL.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">鄒瀾 (圖片來源：中國網)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">至於政策利率，他指，目前人民幣匯率較穩定，美元處於減息通道，匯率不構成很強的外部約束。內部約束方面，去年以來銀行淨息差已出現企穩跡象，連續兩個季度保持1.3厘，今年仍有較大的3年期及5年期等長期存款到期重定價，加上今次下調各類貸款利率，都有助降低銀行付息成本，穩定淨息差，為減息創造一定空間。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">他表示，人行將繼續實施適度寬鬆貨幣政策，加大逆周期及跨周期調節力度，綜合施策，促進社會綜合融資成本在低位運行。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250507_FI_source-ap_PBC-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250507_FI_source-ap_PBC-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">他強調，人行將根據國內外經濟及金融形勢、金融市場運行情況，把促進經濟穩定增長、物價合理回升，作為貨幣政策重要考量，靈活高效運用減息降準在內的措施，保持流動性充裕，保持社會融資條件相對寬鬆，引導金融總量合理增長，信貸均衡投放，令社會融資規模、貨幣供應量增長，與經濟增長及價格總水平預期目標相匹配。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">他又指，要發揮好貨幣政策總量與結構的雙重功能，加快落地近期推出的一系列結構性貨幣政策工具，引導金融機構加力支持擴大內需、科技創新、中小微企業等重點領域。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15584995-%e4%ba%ba%e8%a1%8c%ef%bc%9a%e4%bb%8a%e5%b9%b4%e4%bb%8d%e6%9c%89%e6%b8%9b%e6%81%af%e9%99%8d%e6%ba%96%e7%a9%ba%e9%96%93",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/07/20240710_BLOG_2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-15 15:50:36",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "內地去年新增人民幣貸款16.27萬億元　連續兩年下跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">人民銀行公布，內地去年人民幣新增貸款16.27萬億元(人民幣‧下同)，低於2024年的18.09萬億元，連續兩年下跌。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240415_FI_source-ap_PBC-1.png.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240415_FI_source-ap_PBC-1.png.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">至去年底，人民幣貸款餘額271.91萬億元，按年增長6.4%，略高於市場預期，增速與截至去年11月底相同。廣義貨幣供應量(M2)增長8.5%，增速好過市場預期及去年11月底的8%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">至去年底，社會融資規模存量442.12萬億元，按年增長8.3%。去年全年社會融資規模增量累計35.6萬億元，按年多3.34萬億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">單計去年12月，新增人民幣貸款9100億元，遠好過市場預期的8000億元，社會融資規模增量2.21萬億元，好過預期的2萬億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15584987-%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b0%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e6%96%b0%e5%a2%9e%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e5%b9%a3%e8%b2%b8%e6%ac%be16-27%e8%90%ac%e5%84%84%e5%85%83%e3%80%80%e9%80%a3%e7%ba%8c%e5%85%a9%e5%b9%b4%e4%b8%8b%e8%b7%8c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240415_FI_source-ap_PBC-2.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-15 15:50:38",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "人行：下調各類結構性貨幣政策工具利率0.25厘",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">人民銀行副行長鄒瀾表示，人行將推出兩方面政策措施，下調各類結構性貨幣政策工具利率0.25厘，各類再貸款1年期利率降至1.25厘，其他期限利率同步調整。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">鄒瀾表示，人行將完善結構性工具，並加大支持力度，進一步助力經濟結構轉型優化。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15584920-%e4%ba%ba%e8%a1%8c%ef%bc%9a%e4%b8%8b%e8%aa%bf%e5%90%84%e9%a1%9e%e7%b5%90%e6%a7%8b%e6%80%a7%e8%b2%a8%e5%b9%a3%e6%94%bf%e7%ad%96%e5%b7%a5%e5%85%b7%e5%88%a9%e7%8e%870-25%e5%8e%98",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240415_FI_source-ap_ChinaEco-7.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-15 15:20:35",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "午後改善 滬指收跌13點 深指轉升0.41% 鋰業股反彈",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地A股午後稍微改善，滬市跌幅收窄，深市更倒升收市，兩市交投則回落至不足3萬億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_China-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_China-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指今早低開19點後曾迅速反彈倒升，但在升6點、見4133點便乏力再上，未幾重新轉跌，早市尾段曾失守4100點，最低報4097點，跌28點點，午市雖然全程報跌，但未再跌穿早市低位；滬指最後收報4112點，跌13點或0.33%，成交 1.176萬億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指則於早市初段見全日低位，最低14155點，跌93點，未幾反彈倒升，最高報14328點，升80點，其後反覆回吐又再報跌，午後才有較明顯起色，成功轉升收市；深指收報14306點，升58點或0.41%，成交1.73萬億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數也升9點或0.2%，以4751點收市；創業板指數升18點或0.56%，報3367點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250407_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097181957222-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250407_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097181957222-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">各主要板塊其實跌多於升，重磅銀行股偏軟，農業銀行(01288)A股(601288.SH)跌2.01%，報7.33元；中國銀行(03988)A股(601988.SH)則跌0.73%，報5.43元；建設銀行(00939)A股(601939.SH)跌0.44%，報9.03元；工商銀行(01398)A股(601398.SH)微跌0.13%，報7.68元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">鋰業股反彈，贛鋒鋰業(01772)A股(002460.SZ)漲4.26%，報72元；天齊鋰業(09696)A股(002466.SZ)升2.51%，報61.32元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15584879-%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e6%94%b9%e5%96%84-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c13%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%8c%87%e8%bd%89%e5%8d%870-41-%e9%8b%b0%e6%a5%ad%e8%82%a1%e5%8f%8d%e5%bd%88",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-8.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-15 15:15:44",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
